<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Employee Vendor & Expense Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .landing-page {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        h1, h2, h4, h6, p {
            color: #333;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .features ul, .benefits ul, .getting-started ol {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin-left: 20px;
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .benefits ul {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        .benefits, .getting-started, .support {
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .support {
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .start-now {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="landing-page">
        <center>
            <div class="logo">
            <img src="~/theme/assets/images/logo.png" alt="Rize Stacked Logo" height="200" width="200">
        </div>
        <br />
        <br />
        <div class="description">
            <h3>Welcome to the Employee Vendor & Expense Portal!</h3>
            <p>🌟 Your one-stop destination for all financial management needs!</p>
        </div></center>
        <div class="features">
            <h4>Features:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Vendor Management:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Add New Vendors: Simplify your tasks by adding vendors directly through our intuitive form. Keep all vendor details organized and accessible.</li>
                        <li>Edit & Update: Made an error or need to update vendor details? No worries! Edit with ease and keep your vendor list up-to-date.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Expense Requests:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Seamless Submissions: Submit your expense requests with just a few clicks. Attach bills, provide necessary details, and keep track of approvals.</li>
                        <li>History & Tracking: Review past expense submissions, check the status of pending requests, and get real-time updates.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Cost Center Management:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Add & Allocate: Introduce new cost centers or allocate expenses to existing ones to ensure accurate financial reporting.</li>
                        <li>Insights & Reports: Monitor spending, get insights on cost centers' performance, and make data-driven decisions.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="benefits">
            <h4>Benefits:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Efficiency: Reduce paperwork, save time, and enhance productivity with our easy-to-use portal.</li>
                <li>Transparency: Monitor and manage financial details with complete transparency.</li>
                <li>Accessibility: Access the portal anytime, anywhere, ensuring you’re always in control.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="getting-started">
            <h4>Getting Started:</h4>
            <ol>
                <li>Log In with your employee credentials.</li>
                <li>Navigate to the desired section: 'Vendor Management', 'Expense Requests', or 'Cost Center Management'.</li>
                <li>Start managing your tasks seamlessly!</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="support">
            <h4>🛠 Support & Assistance:</h4>
            <p>Facing an issue or need help? Reach out to our dedicated support team through the 'Help & Support' tab or email us at support@rizemtg.com.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="start-now">
            <p>Elevate your financial management experience with the Employee Vendor & Expense Portal. Dive in and simplify your workflow today!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


